title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is located inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data, the system should successfully export data from two tables. The expected result is that the data is exported.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Insert one table into one grid cell. 3. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
